"Minimising the number of the people in charge and educating them The Company restricts access to users’ personal information to those who work directly with users to carry out marketing functions, those who carry out personal information management (such as personnel in charge of privacy protection, etc.), and others who cannot avoid handling personal information due to the nature of their work. "The Company prevents the leakage of information by personnel via the security pledge that all employees must sign as a condition of their employment, and has proper internal procedures in place to inspect the implementation of the privacy policy and employee compliance.
